{"word":"διδάσκω","slug":"διδάσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διδάσϰω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> disco ‘learn, be informed of’] <b><i>teach, instruct</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b><a href='B:470 4:23'>Mt 4:23</a>,</b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> of Jesus in the gospels; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:510 1:1'>Ac 1:1</a>.</b> Of apostles and others:<b> 4:2; 5:21; <a href='B:520 2:21'>Ro 2:21</a>; <a href='B:530 4:17'>1 Cor 4:17</a>; <a href='B:580 3:16'>Col 3:16</a>.</b> Of an <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ impers.\">impers.</a> entity <b><a href='B:530 11:14'>1 Cor 11:14</a>.</b> With double <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <el>ἐδίδασϰεν αὐτοὺς <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πολλά\">πολλά</a></el> <i>he was teaching them many things</i> <b><a href='B:480 4:2'>Mk 4:2</a>; <a href='B:650 5:12'>Hb 5:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:550 1:12'>Gal 1:12</a>; <a href='B:560 4:21'>Eph 4:21</a>; <a href='B:580 2:7'>Col 2:7</a>; <a href='B:600 2:15'>2 Th 2:15</a>.</b> —In wordplay relating to orders given by a superior <b><a href='B:470 28:15'>Mt 28:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διδάσκαλος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διδαχή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}